data.title: Arizona Christian University
data.meta_description: Learn more about the Air Force ROTC program at Arizona Christian University. Prepare for a rewarding career in the U.S. Air Force or Space Force. Enroll Today.
data.text:
Arizona Christian University has a crosstown agreement with Arizona State University—Det 025. Typically, this means you’ll be enrolled as a full time student at Arizona Christian University and take your ROTC classes each week at Arizona State University—Det 025.

Host School

Arizona State University—Det 025

This is a private school.
